name: TMPA TICKET
description:
This is a big thank you to all of you! Thanks for the last 5 months! Thanks to 2000 followers. Thanks to all my collectors. I am more than proud to be part of this amazing community, we are building something bigger! I deeply fell in love with this community and I have so many plans! Cant wait to show the world what is planned!

This "TMPA Ticket" is a ticket to all my other projects! It is also a little sneak peek on what I am currently working on! Early access to all my projects, and much more plans for the holders!

Thank you for your trust and I love being on this journey with you <3
